  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Trial design: a randomized controlled trial.

      Eligibility criteria for participants: patients with primary early stage oral squamous cell
      carcinoma. Exclusion criteria: cancer of the floor of the mouth.

      Interventions: submandibular gland is preserved during neck dissection for patients of the
      experimental group; submandibular gland is removed during neck dissection for patients of the
      control group.

      Primary Parameters: survival rate, mortality rate
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
